Package org.ontal.imgutil.settings

Class ImageRatio

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ontal.imgutil.settings.ImageRatio
  • public class ImageRatio
extends Object
    Image aspect ratio configuration container class used by Settings. Along with normal fields and constructors contains a list of predefined constants of horizontal and vertical oriented ratios for ratio dependent transformations.
    Since:
    May 2012
    Author:
    akaine
